{
  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_1' aria-label=\" Rahul Verma & Ors. versus Rampat Lal Verma & Ors. pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('1','2025','2025_2_1713_1720','2025INSC296'); ><font size='4'> <strong>RAHUL VERMA & ORS.<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>RAMPAT LAL VERMA & ORS. </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 2 S.C.R. 1713</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 296</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010003482025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : J.B. PARDIWALA, R MAHADEVAN</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Issue arose whether the legal heirs of a deceased partner in a partnership firm, being non-signatories to the partnership deed and in the absence of their explicit consent, can still be bound by the arbitration agreement; and whether the right to sue for the rendition to the legal heirs of the deceased partner, entitling them to invoke the arbitration clause in the partnership deed. Headnotes&dagger; Arbitration and Conciliation Act, 1996 &ndash; Arbitration agreement &ndash; Invocation of the arbitration clause in the partnership deed, by the legal heirs of a<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 21-02-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> SPECIAL LEAVE PETITION (CIVIL) No. 4330/2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Dismissed</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('1','2025','2025_2_1713_1720','2025INSC296','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('1','2025','2025_2_1713_1720','2025INSC296','H'); ><i class='fas fa-file-alt me-2'></i>HTML view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_flip('1','2025','2025_2_1713_1720','2025INSC296');><i class='fas fa-book-open me-2' ></i>Flip view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_pdf('1','2025','2025_2_1713_1720','2025INSC296','N'); ><i class='fas fa-file-pdf me-2'></i>PDF</a></div></div>",
